<h2>Experience</h2>
Professor of History and Interdisciplinary Studies
The University of Baltimore
2021-present
<p>As a full professor, I teach 7 courses per academic year, maintain a research and writing agenda, and contribute to shared governance at my institution.</p>

<h3>Associate Professor of History</h3>
The University of Baltimore
2015-2021
<p>Duties included teaching, research, and contributions to shared governance.
Further experience directing the History B.A. program, and the publication of
my second book.</p>

<h3>Assistant Professor of History</h3>
The University of Baltimore
2009-2015
<p>Duties included teaching, research, and contributions to shared governance.
I was director of the History B.A. program at my institution for three years,
and published my first book.</p>

